{{main|List of awards and nominations received by Trisha Yearwood}}

Yearwood has received many awards and nominations. This includes 3 [[Grammy Award]]s,<ref>{{cite web |title=Search results for "Trisha Yearwood" |url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/artists/trisha-yearwood |website=[[Grammy Awards]] |access-date=July 3, 2019}}</ref> 3 [[Academy of Country Music]] awards,<ref name="ACM">{{cite web |title=Search results for "Trisha Yearwood" |url=https://www.acmcountry.com/winners |website=[[Academy of Country Music]] |access-date=July 3, 2019}}</ref> 3 [[Country Music Association]] awards,<ref name="CMA">{{cite web |title=Past Winners and Nominees: Search results for "Trisha Yearwood" |url=https://cmaawards.com/past-winners-and-nominees/?appSession=0239416K5B620TWHQ95988860P6961VDY161UPSO12LCL8RAEPGZF144J7VYF47A87VV94N9853J4HDMR4LDPTZQ15NKA4A4S488KCK916G1MJ32OLK8CW887CC41QIO |website=[[Country Music Association]] |access-date=July 3, 2019}}</ref> and 1 [[Daytime Emmy Awards|Daytime Emmy award]].<ref name="2013win">{{cite web|url=http://abc7.com/archive/9141349|title=Daytime Emmy Awards 2014: Complete list of winners and nominees|work=KABC-TV|publisher=American Broadcasting Company|access-date=May 22, 2018|archive-date=May 16, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516221308/http://abc7.com/archive/9141349/|url-status=dead}}</ref>

